\c 53 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 53\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Gowwummaa Warra Waaqayyo Malee Jiraatanii (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; kun akka qooqa faarfannaa isa "Mahalaat" jedhamee beekameetti faarfatame; mararoo Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Gowwoonni garaa isaaniitti, "Waaqayyo hin jiru" in jedhu; isaan amalli isaanii manca'aa dha, hammina ciiggaasisaa hojjechaa jiru, namni waan gaarii godhu tokko illee hin jiru.
\m \bd 2\bd* Ogeessonni Waaqayyoon barbaadan, yoo jiraatan arguudhaaf jedhee, Waaqayyo bantii waaqaa keessaa, ilmaan namootaa gad in ilaala.
\m \bd 3\bd* hundinuu dugda itti gataniiru, hundinuus wal ga'anii manca'aniiru; namni gaarii godhu tokko illee hin jiru, lakkii, tokko iyyuu hin jiru.
\m \bd 4\bd* Warri hamaa hojjetan hundinuu homaa hin hubatanii? Warri akkuma buddeena nyaatan saba koo nyaatanis, Waaqayyoon hin waammatanii?
\m \bd 5\bd* Kunoo, isaan sun naasuu guddaadhaan, naasuu takkaa ta'ee hin beekneenis in liqimfamu; Waaqayyo lafee warra marsanii si qabanii in bittimse, Waaqayyo waan isaan gateef, ati akka isaan yeellaasifaman in goota.
\m \bd 6\bd* Xiyoon keessaa Israa'eliif fureen utuma ba'ee! Yeroo Waaqayyo saba isaatiif adda kennuuf, Yaaqoob in burraaqa, Israa'el in gammada. 
